T02TD2868E:208a-1: lag pa brdabs pa'i sgras 'jig pa'i //
T02TD2868E:208a-2: rdo rje byab pa'i las tshogs ni //
T02TD2868E:208a-3: rdo rje 'dzin par bsgoms nas kyang //
T02TD2868E:208a-4: bsam rgyu rang gi lag mthil la //
T02TD2868E:208a-5: aa dang ma las dkyil 'khor bskyed //
T02TD2868E:208a-6: ma las sna tshogs rdo rjer bsam //
T02TD2868E:208a-7: mu khyud rdo rje'i bum dkyil la //
T02TD2868E:208a-8: thun mong khyad par gsang sngags bsam //
T02TD2868E:208a-9: sor mo h'um las bde gshegs sku //
T02TD2868E:208a-10: mtshan rnams dag dang yang dag ldan //
T02TD2868E:208a-11: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cus spras //
T02TD2868E:208a-12: me yi mkha' la rnam par bzhugs //
T02TD2868E:208a-13: me dpung chen po'i ting 'dzin gyis //
T02TD2868E:208a-14: nad dang gdon dang dug sogs la //
T02TD2868E:208a-15: lcags kyu'i ting 'dzin sbyor ba yis //
T02TD2868E:208a-16: dbyung ba'i tshul du phyung nas kyang //
T02TD2868E:208a-17: zhi ba'i gzugs brnyan dag la bstim //
T02TD2868E:208a-18: dkar gsum klu sman dag dang bcas //
T02TD2868E:208a-19: gang gnod phyogs su bskyal bar bya //
T02TD2868E:208a-20: mngon spyod drag po'i phrin las ni //
T02TD2868E:208a-21: rdzus skyes tshul du bskyed byas la //
T02TD2868E:208a-22: gang dmigs gzugs dang rten du bcas //
T02TD2868E:208a-23: phyung ste khyad par gsang sngags bzlas //
T02TD2868E:208a-24: bsreg dang sbyang dang brdung byas la //
T02TD2868E:208a-26: rdo rje byab pa'i las tshogs /
T02TD2868E:208a-27: rje btsun klu sgrub kyis mdzad pa rdzogs so//
